# Zero Trust Application Settings

## RustDesk Server Application

```json
{
    "name": "RustDesk Server",
    "domain": "remote.bbj4u.xyz",
    "type": "self_hosted",
    "rules": [
        {
            "name": "Allow Trusted Users",
            "decision": "allow",
            "include": [
                {
                    "email_domain": {
                        "domain": "bbj4u.xyz"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "geo": {
                        "country_code": "US"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "require": [
                {
                    "auth_method": ["device_posture"]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

## Trae.ai IDE Application

```json
{
    "name": "Trae.ai IDE",
    "domain": "trae.bbj4u.xyz",
    "type": "self_hosted",
    "session_duration": "24h",
    "rules": [
        {
            "name": "Allow Developers",
            "decision": "allow",
            "include": [
                {
                    "group": "Developers"
                }
            ],
            "require": [
                {
                    "auth_method": ["device_posture", "github"]
                },
                {
                    "geo": {
                        "country_code": "US"
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "auto_redirect_to_identity": true
}
```
